08:55.269 --> 08:57.830
All right, just take your gear
up to the bathroom.

08:57.909 --> 09:01.939
- Al, maybe you can help me.
- Like he's gonna know anything.

09:02.030 --> 09:04.100
Come here.
Come here, come here.

09:04.749 --> 09:08.060
Which one of these colors do you like?

09:09.469 --> 09:12.100
I like the loquat or the kumquat.

09:12.189 --> 09:16.340
Come oﬀ of it, Al. Like you can
