09:35.909 --> 09:38.939
Today is a special program -
it takes place in my own home.

09:39.030 --> 09:41.739
Here's my lovely wife. Jill.

09:44.989 --> 09:47.290
And of course.
we all know my assistant.

09:47.390 --> 09:49.580
Howdy.Doody,

09:49.669 --> 09:50.979
follow me this way.

09:51.070 --> 09:54.459
