12:09.110 --> 12:10.820
three,

12:10.910 --> 12:12.300
two,

12:12.389 --> 12:13.700
one.

12:13.789 --> 12:16.139
We're in the final step
of our bathroom redo,

12:16.229 --> 12:19.340
and that's where we install
