17:29.720 --> 17:32.630
- Hi-ho, Tim.
- Hi, Wilson.

17:32.720 --> 17:37.150
- Get your water back on?
- finally. Here's your end of the hose.

17:37.240 --> 17:40.549
Thank you, neighbor.
Beautiful night, isn't it?

17:40.640 --> 17:44.990
- Crisp, clear and cold.
- What are you up to?

17:45.079 --> 17:48.509
Just checking
the expanding universe, Tim.

17:49.039 --> 17:53.430
- You got a minute?
